properties.name: Path
properties.expression: const sourcePath = thisLayer.content('Limb').content('Base').content('Path').path;const tot = thisProperty.propertyGroup(4)(1).name.split(' ')[1];const place = clamp(1 / tot * thisProperty.propertyGroup(3).name.split(' ')[1], 0.001, 0.999) - (0.5 / tot);const leng = linear(place, 0, 1, thisLayer.effect('Doyouthinkhesaurus')('Start Length').value, thisLayer.effect('Doyouthinkhesaurus')('End Length').value) * thisLayer.content('Admin').content('Scaling Factors').transform.scale[0];const flip = (thisLayer.effect('Doyouthinkhesaurus')('Flip side') - 0.5) * 2;const normal = sourcePath.normalOnPath(place);const ps = sourcePath.pointOnPath(place) - normal * thisLayer.content('Limb').content('Base').content('Stroke 1').strokeWidth * (1 - place) * 0.5 * thisLayer.effect('Doyouthinkhesaurus')('Center Offset') * 0.01 * flip;createPath([ps, ps - normal * leng * flip], [], [], false)

properties.name: Path
properties.expression: function limbPath() {        // Limber Path Limb        const thisProp = thisProperty;        const endctrl = thisComp.layer('{{ end }}');        const curveLin = endctrl('ADBE Effect Parade')('Pseudo/skl_main_data_01')('curvature').value[1] * 0.01;        if (curveLin === 0) {            return createPath([                endctrl('ADBE Effect Parade')('Pseudo/skl_main_data_01')('p0').value,                endctrl('ADBE Effect Parade')('Pseudo/skl_main_data_01')('p1ikfkfreek').value,                endctrl('ADBE Effect Parade')('Pseudo/skl_main_data_01')('p2ikfkfreek').value,            ], [], [], false);        }        else {            const inTangPos = endctrl('ADBE Effect Parade')('Pseudo/skl_main_data_01')('inTangPos').value;            const outTangPos = endctrl('ADBE Effect Parade')('Pseudo/skl_main_data_01')('outTangPos').value;            return createPath([                endctrl('ADBE Effect Parade')('Pseudo/skl_main_data_01')('p0').value,                endctrl('ADBE Effect Parade')('Pseudo/skl_main_data_01')('p1ikfkfreek').value,                endctrl('ADBE Effect Parade')('Pseudo/skl_main_data_01')('p2ikfkfreek').value,            ], [[0, 0], inTangPos, [0, 0]], [[0, 0], mul(outTangPos, -1), [0, 0]], false);        }    }limbPath();// Limber Library limbPath

properties.name: Scale
properties.expression: const endctrl = thisComp.layer('{{ end }}');const scaleFactor = endctrl.effect('Pseudo/skl_main_data_01')('scaleFactor').value[0];const widthScale = endctrl.effect('Limber')('Width Scale') * 0.01;[scaleFactor * widthScale, 0]

properties.name: Scale
Position
properties.expression: let val = [0, 0];if (thisLayer.hasParent) val = thisLayer.parent.fromWorld([0, 0, 0]);[val[0], val[1], 0];

properties.name: Scale
properties.expression: let val = [100, 100]if (thisLayer.hasParent) {    const ctrlScaleFactor = Math.max(length(thisLayer.toComp([0, 0]), thisLayer.toComp([0.7071, 0.7071])), 0.0001);    val = [value[0] / ctrlScaleFactor, value[1] / ctrlScaleFactor]}val

properties.name: Rotation
properties.expression: let val = 0;if (thisLayer.hasParent) {    const vec = thisLayer.parent.toWorldVec([1, 0, 0]);    val = -radiansToDegrees(Math.atan2(vec[1], vec[0]))}val
